{"tid":2478743,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 真人經歷 ]  自細有陰陽眼 尖沙咀某地方超多靈體..","createTime":"2021-04-07T09:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T09:49:59.000Z","uid":82845,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a80efb1d4bd06f3f04da3644c762c5d6651395b","tid":2478743,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n小弟由細到大都有陰陽眼, 其實鬼處處都有, 但如果講到多鬼, 我一定要同大家分享尖沙咀某一個地方, 呢個地方唔近海邊, 佢個位置係夾係喺兩個商場中間, 而你去得個度你都一定要行落地牢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解我會話呢個area多鬼, 事關我曾經喺個個地方既前一身(大約13-16年)返過兩年part time, 以前呢個地方係賣既野同埋氣氛同而家都差好遠, 以前整體都係陰陰暗暗, 平日人流唔算多. 我個陣返工成日都會見到啲「人」行黎行去, 仲試過唔小心誤會左佢地係真既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有次我試過Serve完個客, 佢同我講件貨唔要了, 我Serve完佢, 我同事行埋黎問我, 你岩岩同邊個講野, 我就同佢講返有個客岩岩試衫試完唔要~ 佢同我講, 佢從來都見唔到有人喺我則邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有試過去個個地方既洗手間既時候, 見到男廁有個著紅衫長髮既女人企左喺度, 清潔工都係度, 但佢完全冇理到佢, 當我柯完尿之後, 個個女人就消失左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為見慣我都不怪, 最恐怖既一次係有次返貨倉執緊貨個陣, 忽然有人好大聲咁叫我個中文全名, 而當時貨倉得我一個人, 而貨倉出面亦冇人喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多芝麻細碎 收錄唔曬 其實呢個地方因為長年累月都冇陽光, 所以陰氣超重. 即使而家已經轉左型, 成個場都好光猛又播好多好活力既音樂也好, 我每次去到都見到好多重重黑影...<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\"><span class=\"pink\">唔怪得我去果度成日FEEL到有野</span></span>....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a8a5b0d0549f9525e893247b730d6aff70fc2be","tid":2478743,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"即係邊到"},{"pid":"2c00db7234d2fd6820f96d0737fff1c50d107b96","tid":2478743,"uid":39320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:43:26.000Z","msg":"開名啦"},{"pid":"c51361fd090cdbb59231227d2b3adbd961499f89","tid":2478743,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a8a5b0d0549f9525e893247b730d6aff70fc2be","tid":2478743,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"即係邊到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"咁都唔知，尖沙咀果度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd18d4673f149dfca4978bea3240e033d3010a24","tid":2478743,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c51361fd090cdbb59231227d2b3adbd961499f89","tid":2478743,"uid":287107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a8a5b0d0549f9525e893247b730d6aff70fc2be","tid":2478743,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:42:42.000Z","msg":"即係邊到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:46:14.000Z","msg":"咁都唔知，尖沙咀果度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:47:35.000Z","msg":"淨係覺得尖東海傍好邪，其他地方唔太覺"},{"pid":"503beb1571c4950ad377d01a195e8175e3b2b8e0","tid":2478743,"uid":263409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"Mira?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85229dc32779a50d83218ca75ebe261651453f51","tid":2478743,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係donki<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59de3b9d4ebd7290dda8535a113c7c564b8087c","tid":2478743,"uid":131148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85229dc32779a50d83218ca75ebe261651453f51","tid":2478743,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"係唔係donki<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T09:49:34.000Z","msg":"係嚕，前身好似係collect point"},{"pid":"128716fcf50b856a90c92729259686c061e73d7d","tid":2478743,"uid":209773,"like